node.text: Today is a great day to start to taking steps to create change for Mother Earth. Please join @tentree and I in planting 50,000 trees. I know the words eco friendly or going green can be scary or hopeless but today we can make it easy...if you purchase the “Brie Bella Planting Package” on the tentree site you’ll be making an impactful change by planting trees. Head to my stories to understand how trees do more than being carbon neutral and head to the link in bio to join me on making this planet healthier. ✨

node.text: I’ll never forget the day @thenikkibella and I got the call that @latina magazine wants us on the cover!!! 🥰 We fell in love with this magazine when we were in middle school because it was women who reminded us of what we saw in the mirror!!! @jlo was the first one to grace the cover after filming Selena (one of my idols). It opened up a whole world of securities for us latina girls. I might not be full but the parts I am I’m so proud of! Thank you Dad for always representing the Latin culture and educating us kids on it!! My little Bird looks forward to all of her Tata’s Spanish videos. My Dad  @jegarcia64 only speaks Spanish to the grandkids so that they know Mexican blood runs through them. Here’s to #hispanicheritagemonth ❤️🙌🏽
